    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six power plant. This specimen boasts a seamless power band thanks to its six individual throttle bodies and a fully serviced dual-VANOS system. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile engagement, paired with a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential for superior corner-exit traction. The chassis is structurally pristine with proactive rear subframe reinforcement already completed. Finished in flawless Carbon Black, the exterior reflects a deep, swirl-free luster, while the interior remains preserved with supple Nappa leather and zero bolster wear. This is a mechanically sorted, collector-quality example with a comprehensive service dossier.",
